            "title": "A股午後向上   兩市成交近25000億人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股午後上揚，破上午高位，深股全日報跌，兩市成交合計24880.24億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-3.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-3.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指全日報4162點，升16點或0.39%，今早開見4128，跌18點或0.43%，為全日低，其後跌幅收窄，午後顯著向上，升破上午高位，最高見4166，升20點或0.48%，為全日高位，全日成交10723.68億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指半日報14495點，跌8點或0.06%，最低見14366，跌137點或0.94%，跌幅其後收窄，午後高見14497，僅跌6點或0.04%，為全日高位，全日成交14156.56億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300全日跌16點或0.34%，報4710點 ; 創業板指數跌34點或1.04%，報3310點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">與春節假期前比較，滬指累升84點或2.06%，深成指累升395點或2.8%。</p>\n</div>",
